### Player Endpoints

### Get all players
GET http://localhost:8080/players

### Get player by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/players/1

### Create new player
POST http://localhost:8080/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Max Mustermann",
  "pointsEarned": 0,
  "teamId": 1
}

### Create another player
POST http://localhost:8080/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Erika Musterfrau",
  "pointsEarned": 150,
  "teamId": 1
}

### Update player
PUT http://localhost:8080/players/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Max Mustermann",
  "pointsEarned": 250,
  "teamId": 1
}

### Delete player by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/players/1

### Delete all players
DELETE http://localhost:8080/players

