### Word Endpoints

### Get all words
GET http://localhost:8080/words

### Get word by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/words/1

### Get words by category
GET http://localhost:8080/words/category/EASY

### Get words by category - MEDIUM
GET http://localhost:8080/words/category/MEDIUM

### Get words by category - HARD
GET http://localhost:8080/words/category/HARD

### Create new word - EASY
POST http://localhost:8080/words
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "word": "Apfel",
  "definition": "Eine runde Frucht",
  "points": 10,
  "category": "EASY"
}

